            Over the years, as the law has advanced in all kinds of areas&#x2014;personal liability, corporate liability, human rights and so on&#x2014;the necessary consequential amendments have been made to other legislation. That
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_383gc' title='Col. 383GC &mdash; HL Deb 19 May 2004 vol 661 c383GC' name='column_383gc' href='#column_383gc' rel='bookmark'>383GC</a>
            may not cover the noble Baroness's legitimate question; I shall take advice and try to write to her. I shall certainly have an answer in advance of the next stage.
          </p>
